{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261428, "create_time": 1656390897, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "来自招生时一个同学的提问，竟然无法回答", "timestamp": 1656390897}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261436, "create_time": 1656391083, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "计算机有什么意义？能赚大钱。赚大钱有什么意义？赚大钱能买大房子豪车。为什么要买大房子豪车？买大房子豪车能让我的生活更加舒服。为什么生活就因此更舒服了呢？", "timestamp": 1656391083}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261441, "create_time": 1656391414, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得计算机学了之后工作还是比较有成就感的", "timestamp": 1656391414}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261449, "create_time": 1656391536, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 你现在用的树洞、手机上的软件都几乎是学计算机相关专业的人开发的。当然，学数学也能自学这些东西。", "timestamp": 1656391536}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261451, "create_time": 1656391578, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 那可以进一步追问：计算机的成就感来自于哪里？是自己解决了一个工程问题本身？还是解决了工程问题所带来的报酬？我觉得引导招生同学去自我追问是一个有效手段", "timestamp": 1656391578}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261455, "create_time": 1656391593, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 不是说对个人的意义\n工科商科都是投入到实际应用带来生产力的\n基础数学现在研究的东西基本都是空中楼阁吧", "timestamp": 1656391593}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261460, "create_time": 1656391650, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 不想开地图炮，但是就我看到的学弟学妹都是认为计算机“钱途光明”才选的计算机，对于技术的热爱不是主要的", "timestamp": 1656391650}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261464, "create_time": 1656391725, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 我懂你说的，一个专业你要能愿意不为绩点地投入去学习、甚至愿意之后以此为业，还是要能告诉自己一个能自圆其说的故事", "timestamp": 1656391725}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261466, "create_time": 1656391783, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 我就是想表达这个意思", "timestamp": 1656391783}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261467, "create_time": 1656391804, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 是啊，不过对这种同学也应该鼓励学计算机啊，如果没什么特殊偏好的话至少学个有钱途的工作", "timestamp": 1656391804}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261468, "create_time": 1656391849, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "*专业", "timestamp": 1656391849}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261471, "create_time": 1656391881, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "这个同学表示想学基础数学，但他的想法总觉得是基础数学能给社会带来生产力，能带来很多应用；我又不好说实际上真正的基础数学基本停留在理论阶段，所谓数学带来应用其实都是工科里面使用的数学，其实和数学前沿差很远。。。。。。", "timestamp": 1656391881}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261473, "create_time": 1656391934, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 唉。高中的小朋友们哪有机会了解各个专业的状况啊……用这短短一个月不到的时间决定自己以后从事的行业太草率了", "timestamp": 1656391934}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261474, "create_time": 1656391947, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得高中生很多是真的对大部分的学科没接触过，也不会有什么特别的兴趣，那就都选计算机也挺好的", "timestamp": 1656391947}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261476, "create_time": 1656391982, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 是的啊", "timestamp": 1656391982}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261478, "create_time": 1656392040, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 确实，不过选别的专业后来想转计算机的多的是，还不如一步到位", "timestamp": 1656392040}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261480, "create_time": 1656392053, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "dz也是本来想大一为了以后待遇转计算机的，结果感觉自己并不喜欢敲代码就quit了这个想法\n但是这些事情和学弟学妹说完全没有意义，因为他们根本不了解", "timestamp": 1656392053}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261599, "create_time": 1656395372, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 冠冕堂皇的话当然是“拓展人类认知边界”、“为了人类心智的荣耀”blabla，实际中我觉得基础数学从业者主要是起到一个学术传承的作用，研究只是附带的，同时起到一个抽奖的作用。否则用不了几代人那些高深的知识就没人能看懂了...", "timestamp": 1656395372}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261603, "create_time": 1656395772, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "为往圣继绝学", "timestamp": 1656395772}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 261660, "create_time": 1656397567, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 他的想法不错。不过促进生产力环节不一定由他完成，而是其他人。", "timestamp": 1656397567}], "create_time": 1656390864, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1656397567, "likenum": 10, "n_attentions": 10, "n_comments": 20, "pid": 74147, "poll": null, "reply": 20, "text": "基础数学研究的意义何在呢", "timestamp": 1656390864}}